---
title: BBQ Spiced Double Salmon with Red Onion and Apple Salad
description: BBQ-seasoned salmon tops this summer-inspired delight! Quick roasted sweet onions get tossed with slivers of crisp apples, toasted almonds and spring mix. A simple oil and vinegar dressing is all you need to bring this whole dish together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/double-saumon-aux-epices-bbq-60b13d79.jpg
